    public class JsoupRawStringSampler
extends JsoupElementBasedSampler<JsoupDocumentSampler,org.jsoup.nodes.Document,String>
    Strips the Jsoup boiler plate and returns just the raw text from the response. Useful for non-HTML samples.
    Since:
    3.0.0
